<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="15Nov1919"><font color="red">15 November 1919</font>, <cite>Yale</cite> (JJ to Ezra Pound): As there is nothing to be hoped for from Mr Quinn I wrote urgently to my agent Mr Pinker &hellip; asking him to cable Huebsch for an advance of royalties on any or all of my books &hellip; Will you please send me the last number of the <cite>Little Review</cite>.</div>
